    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, dependable ride that gets the job done? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it's got some miles on it and you'll notice a few cosmetic blemishes and the expected wear that comes with a well-used vehicle. Mechanically, it's still running and ready to take you where you need to go. If you're after a practical, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left in it, this could be your perfect match!",
      "price": 21000.0,
